---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const appStoreUrl = "https://apps.apple.com/app/picovoice/id6759188352";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How to Sell VTuber Voice Clips | PicoVoice"
  description="A step-by-step guide to selling short voice clips on PicoVoice — record, set pricing, publish, and earn."
  path="/en/how-to-sell-vtuber-voice"
  type="article"
  lang="en"
  alternatePath="/how-to-sell-vtuber-voice"
>
  <section class="content-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">How-To Guide</p>
    <h1>How to Sell VTuber Voice Clips</h1>
    <p class="content-hero-lead">A complete guide to publishing and selling short voice clips on PicoVoice.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>Selling Steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Record</strong> — Create a voice clip of approximately 30 seconds. You can record directly in the app — no external tools required.</li>
      <li><strong>Set Details</strong> — Add a title and description. The publication period is fixed at one week.</li>
      <li><strong>Configure Pricing</strong> — Set price tiers for Streaming (in-app playback) and Download (file save) separately.</li>
      <li><strong>Submit for Review</strong> — After passing review, your listing goes live automatically.</li>
      <li><strong>Promote</strong> — Share your listing link on social media or during livestreams to reach fans.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>From Sale to Payout</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Set your price</strong> — Choose from 5 price tiers each for Streaming (in-app playback) and Download (file save).</li>
      <li><strong>Fans purchase</strong> — Transactions are processed via App Store in-app purchases.</li>
      <li><strong>Fees are deducted</strong> — Apple's commission (15–30%) is deducted first, then PicoVoice takes a 10% platform fee from the post-Apple amount.</li>
      <li><strong>Receive your earnings</strong> — You keep 90% of the post-Apple amount. Payouts are made via bank transfer once your balance reaches ¥10,000.</li>
    </ol>
    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: var(--space-sm);">* Apple Small Business Program members pay a 15% commission. Exact tier prices may vary based on Apple's pricing.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>Tips for Success</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Descriptive titles</strong> — Use titles that clearly convey the intended use (e.g., "Morning Alarm", "Cheer Message", "Goodnight Voice")</li>
      <li><strong>Leverage the one-week window</strong> — The fixed one-week publication period creates natural scarcity and urgency that drives purchases</li>
      <li><strong>Create a series</strong> — Publishing regularly builds ongoing fan engagement and repeat purchases</li>
      <li><strong>Leverage your community</strong> — Announce new drops during streams or on social media for maximum visibility</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="content-cta">
    <h2>Start Selling Your Voice</h2>
    <p>Download PicoVoice and start monetizing your voice clips today.</p>
    <a class="cta cta-coral" href={appStoreUrl} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Get Free on App Store</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, #fff 0%, #fbf9ff 45%, #fff4f7 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px var(--shadow-purple);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .content-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .content-hero-lead {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .content-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px var(--shadow-color);
  }
  .content-card h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .content-card li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .content-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fff 0%, #f6f2ff 50%, #fff4f7 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .content-cta h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .content-cta p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
